	<h2><em>About Us </em></h2>
	
	<p>Mental health! These two words are heard a lot now – a – days. 
	There is a lot of awareness being created on the importance of a healthy mind. 
	But is only creating an awareness enough? 
	Here, we present to you our all in one WebApp where you can speak to doctors from the comfort of your room about both- physical and mental issues, get assistance from them as and when required, chat with other people in the mental health community and also find some great yoga techniques to keep your mind and body calm. 
	What are you waiting for? Are afraid of being interrupted by a third – party? Don’t worry. We promise to never use your data without your permission. Also, we assure you of secured one – on – one communication with the docs.
	</p>

