<br>	<br><br><h1><em>Why should you volunteer as a doc here?</em></h1>

	<p>Help the community to be a better and healthier place. As a doctor, you have a lot of responsibilities and we understand that. Here, we are adding on to that list of responsibilities by asking you to join this wonderful community where we help people to open up about their mental and physical illnesses. 
	The reason we have created this community is to give people a secured and a comfortable place to speak about the issues that they face, especially the ones related to mental health. 
	Also you don't need to be there all time on this website you can login whenever you are free to give advices to one's who need it.
